---
import DefaultLayout from "../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro";
---

<DefaultLayout title="Hubungi Jasa Vote | Kontak Admin Resmi" description="Hubungi layanan Jasa Vote untuk konsultasi kompetisi, polling, dan peningkatan interaksi sosial media Anda. Fast response 24 jam.">
  <section class="contact-section">
    <div class="contact-container">
      <h1>Hubungi Jasa Vote</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Konsultasikan kebutuhan campaign, kontes, polling, dan jasa vote Anda bersama tim ahli kami. Kami siap melayani 24 jam penuh.</p>

      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div class="contact-card wa">
          <div class="icon">💬</div>
          <h3>WhatsApp</h3>
          <p>Fast response dan siap melayani konsultasi mendesak 24 jam.</p>
          <a href="https://wa.me/6289634740308?text=hallo%20admin%20saya%20mau%20jasa%20vote" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-contact">Chat Sekarang</a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card tg">
          <div class="icon">✈️</div>
          <h3>Telegram</h3>
          <p>Alternatif komunikasi cepat, aman, dan fleksibel.</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn-contact">Buka Telegram</a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card mail">
          <div class="icon">✉️</div>
          <h3>Email</h3>
          <p>Untuk kebutuhan bisnis, kerja sama jangka panjang, dan partnership.</p>
          <a href="mailto:support@jasavote.my.id" class="btn-contact">Kirim Email</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>⏰ Jam Operasional</h3>
        <p>Senin - Minggu: <strong>24 Jam Nonstop</strong></p>
        <p><em>Butuh Respon Cepat? Silakan klik tombol WhatsApp untuk langsung terhubung dengan admin yang sedang bertugas.</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</htmlLayout>

<style>
  .contact-section {
    padding: 60px 20px;
    background: #f8fafc;
    min-height: 70vh;
  }
  .contact-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #0f172a;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: #475569;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 50px auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 25px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }
  .contact-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 30px 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .contact-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }
  .icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }
  .contact-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .contact-card p {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .btn-contact {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px;
    background: #0284c7;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .contact-card.wa .btn-contact { background: #22c55e; }
  .contact-card.wa .btn-contact:hover { background: #16a34a; }
  .contact-card.tg .btn-contact { background: #0ea5e9; }
  .contact-card.tg .btn-contact:hover { background: #0284c7; }
  .contact-card.mail .btn-contact { background: #64748b; }
  .contact-card.mail .btn-contact:hover { background: #475569; }
  
  .info-box {
    background: #e0f2fe;
    border-left: 5px solid #0284c7;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
    color: #0369a1;
  }
  .info-box h3 { margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .info-box p { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5; }
</style>

